<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.6.6">
<l>tīnīr vaṇṇa māma larkoṇṭu viraiyēnti</l>
<l>tūnīr paravit toḻumi ṉeḻumiṉ toṇṭīrkāḷ</l>
<l>mānīr vaṇṇar maruvi yuṟaiyu miṭamvāṉil</l>
<l>kūṉīr matiyai māṭan tīṇṭuṅ kuṟuṅkuṭiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You of purity, worship praising [him], bearing incense</l>
<l>[And] bringing fire, water, [and] beautiful, large flowers.</l>
<l>Devotees, set out to Kuṟuṅkuṭi where mansions touch</l>
<l rend="indent">the curve-shaped moon in the sky,</l>
<l>The place the one the color of the great [ocean] water dwells fondly.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
